{"tid":2393765,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"[AndThen.hk] 封區效果：北角黃店街被突襲後 生意暴跌得番一成","createTime":"2021-02-03T16:55:37.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-04T04:57:51.000Z","uid":48083,"like":7,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"d33c0e5d7698d1e4f563ce1905f62d6687679abf","tid":2393765,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-03T16:55:37.000Z","msg":"︱#北角有條黃店街︱<br />\n<br />\n近日政府突襲封區，早前北角的「黃店街」也首當其衝。人稱「黃店街」的北角錦屏後街，短短的巷仔已經有至少7間良心小店藏身其中，政府封區期間，其中一間小店 Villa Villa Cafe &amp; Bar 的8位員工更被票控，引起網民關注。<br />\n<br />\nAndThen記者於解封之後特意前往這裡，看看疫情、封區之後小店的生意狀況。記者抵達時正值下午，但只有 The Beans 北豆 、 酒盜 兩間小店營業， 古月 Ancient Moon 、Villa Villa等小店則未有營業。<br />\n<br />\n北豆的負責人蔡小姐表示疫情之後，舖頭生意銳減跌至一成，每日只得幾百至一千的生意額，曾經一度需要告急，面臨結業危機。幸在告急後，得到不少同路人以外賣形式支持，又有有心人邀請合辦市集，店舖才能夠堅持至今。她又指出其他「鄰居」亦面對相似的困境，Villa Villa的情況在當中算是最好，訪問最後她表示：「多謝大家一路以來撐住北豆，新一年希望大家能平平安安，同路人北豆見。」<br />\n<br />\n【其他文章推薦】<br />\n傅珮嘉灣仔新開台菜：<a href=\"http://bit.ly/3nvH9M0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F3nvH9M0&d=f02Xtm2mX5FaAGCExHUdjSNNnhsiPIcvur842Fp1uB0%3D&h=1e12c7af\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">bit.ly/3nvH9M0</a><br />\n太子點心店正向抗疫：<a href=\"http://bit.ly/391CfSM\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F391CfSM&d=f02Xtm2mX5FaAGCExHUdjSNNnhsiPIcvur842Fp1uB0%3D&h=234564d1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">bit.ly/391CfSM</a><br />\n<br />\n#AndThenHK跟住去 #和你一起 #好好過活<br />\n💛FOLLOW <a href=\"http://AndThen.hk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2FAndThen.hk&d=f02Xtm2mX5FaAGCExHUdjSNNnhsiPIcvur842Fp1uB0%3D&h=5c811bed\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">AndThen.hk</a><br />\n📘Facebook: <a href=\"http://facebook.com/andthenhk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ffacebook.com%2Fandthenhk&d=f02Xtm2mX5FaAGCExHUdjSNNnhsiPIcvur842Fp1uB0%3D&h=23ff4311\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">facebook.com/andthenhk</a><br />\n📷Instagram: <a href=\"http://instagram.com/andthenhk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi